    },
    {
      "id": "6a2068201280f0000000f1cd94",
      "text": "第23週: 日月火水[[木]]金土",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780508705,
      "updated": 1780508705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2068201280f000000013198a",
      "text": "2026年 42.47％経過",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780508705,
      "updated": 1780508705
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2065df00000000008fe8f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508127,
      "updated": 1780508127
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2065df00000000008fe8f3",
      "text": "[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508127,
      "updated": 1780508128
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2065e000000000008fe8f5",
      "text": "\t[井戸端荘]、少女とロボット(?)x2と鳥x2",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508128,
      "updated": 1780508344
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20660f00000000008fe8f6",
      "text": "\t\tstaだけ男",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508176,
      "updated": 1780508179
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20661300000000008fe8f7",
      "text": "\t\tこれは... 主人公なのでは... www",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780508179,
      "updated": 1780508190
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20682400000000009226c7",
      "text": "\t\t大爆笑[takker.icon][inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780508709,
      "updated": 1780520588
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20867d000000000092fd3d",
      "text": "\t\t僕好みはなろう系よろしくハーレム（人間以外から好かれるも含む）だけど、井戸端の良さも薄まる気がするなぁ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516477,
      "updated": 1780516519
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2065df00000000008fe8f4",
      "text": "\t\t[お当番回]感ある[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780508128,
      "updated": 1780520624
    },
    {
      "id": "6a209692000000000076d9b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780520594,
      "updated": 1780520594
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208a02000000000092fd45",
      "text": "[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517378,
      "updated": 1780517378
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208a02000000000092fd46",
      "text": "\t新しい扉が開きそうな予感",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517379,
      "updated": 1780517465
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208a06000000000092fd48",
      "text": "\t\t長らくなろう系に毒されていて、いかに主人公への好意を最大化するかがカタルシスだったのだけど、井戸端荘だと中和される",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517382,
      "updated": 1780517642
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208a36000000000092fd49",
      "text": "\t\t個が共存しつつも、我も出せる塩梅",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517430,
      "updated": 1780517456
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208a50000000000092fd4a",
      "text": "\t\t令和のカタルシス、は言い過ぎかもだが",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517456,
      "updated": 1780517708
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208b2b000000000092fd50",
      "text": "\t[我々の文明では、性欲 = 情報共有欲です]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517675,
      "updated": 1780517707
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208aa2000000000092fd4d",
      "text": "\t\t非言語情報と言語情報の違いかもしれないな",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517538,
      "updated": 1780517547
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208aab000000000092fd4e",
      "text": "\t\t人間の文明だと前者",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780517547,
      "updated": 1780517567
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208aa0000000000092fd4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
